data.description: Nestled in a picturesque tree-lined neighborhood, this magnificent home is the epitome of comfort and relaxation. Upon entering, you step into a spacious and open foyer that sets the tone for the rest of the home. The interior is thoughtfully designed with a seamless flow between the various living areas, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. As you make your way through the living areas, you're drawn to the family room, complete with a fireplace that adds a touch of coziness. Now, let's step outside to the backyard paradise! The centerpiece is a crystal-clear, shimmering pool, surrounded by a lush green lawn, flanked by majestic lemon and orange trees. Adjacent to the pool, you'll find a pool house that serves as a versatile retreat. For those seeking respite from the sun, a large, covered patio beckons. This enchanting residence is where you can make cherished memories, with family and friends! Get a $4,000 credit for your closing costs!
